trans-unit.source: The basic 256-bit security algorithm suite.

trans-unit.source: The asymmetric key length.
trans-unit.target: 非對稱金鑰長度。

trans-unit.source: Returns <see langword="true" /> if the specified asymmetric key length is supported; otherwise, returns <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果支援指定的非對稱金鑰長度，則會傳回 <see langword="true" />，否則會傳回 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Valid lengths range from 1024 to 4096.
trans-unit.target: 有效長度範圍為 1024 到 4096。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified asymmetric key length is supported; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果支援指定的非對稱金鑰長度，則為 <see langword="true" />，否則為 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The symmetric key length.

trans-unit.target: 如果支援指定的對稱金鑰長度，則會傳回 <see langword="true" />，否則會傳回 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The only valid length is 256.
trans-unit.target: 唯一有效長度是 256。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the specified symmetric key length is supported; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
